answers.answer: Hi there, the best range for these numbers is to be mid range.  Your appear to be about double what they should be though I don't know what the range for your lab is.There are a lot of things that can affect your numbers.  Alcohol is a big one, medication can also affect the AST ALT.  When elevated they are indicating that your liver is inflamed.How do you feel?Have you had any other tests done?

title: What are the optimum SGOT and SGPT levels ?
